EBS Universität für Wirtschaft und Recht

Renowned since 1971

   EBS Universität is the oldest private business university in Germany,
   and our alumni have been successful all over the world for more than 40
   years. The reason lies in our concept: Under the common name of EBS
   Universität, our faculties EBS Law School, EBS Business School and EBS
   Executive School combine scientifically grounded education with
   innovative concepts and particularly intensive support and
   encouragement for each individual student. The Faculties of economics,
   law and continuing education work together synergistically and form a
   strong foundation for innovative research as well as for your
   practice-oriented education and training.

   At EBS Universität you will acquire the professional and personal
   know-how to successfully master professional challenges. Across all our
   courses of study we are committed to:
     * Scientific excellence
     * Internationality
     * Practical relevance
     * Personality development
     * Interdisciplinary thinking
     * Social responsibility
     * Lifelong learning

   Due to its understanding of excellence, EBS Universität appeals to
   students and professors who are talented and enthusiastic, efficient
   and creative.

